{"tid":1473795,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"4大通訊軟件，無懼斷網 ，大家會唔會用？","createTime":"2019-08-15T03:06:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T11:04:42.000Z","uid":110313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"08e799c9537a34b4c5846226e5ca68c1e2ca9264","tid":1473795,"uid":110313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:06:11.000Z","msg":"【#BF商業視野】4大通訊軟件，無懼斷網！<br />\n<br />\n一去到人多的地方，網絡就會收得好差，難以及時接收訊息。若遇上斷網情況，市民又有何方法解決？以下有4個通訊軟件：Bridgefy、Zello、iNtercom、FireChat，均允許在無網絡下通訊。<br />\n<br />\n1. Bridgefy<br />\n<br />\n此應用程式使用藍牙向周圍的用戶發送訊息，即使無Wi-Fi、3G/4G 流動網絡也可傳送訊息。程式有一對一聊天模式，能與距離不到100公尺的朋友進行對話；廣播模式（Broadcast），可以同時向周圍所有使用 Bridgefy的用戶傳送訊息，包括非聯絡人。<br />\n<br />\n網狀網絡模式（Mesh Mode）則可透過中間點，即另1位Bridgefy用家，將傳送訊息範圍廷伸至200米內，中間點使用者不會看到該訊息。另有線上模式（Online Mode） 可在連接網路時使用，以及可點擊聊天畫面上的萬字夾按鈕，發送自己的定位位置。<br />\n<br />\n2. Zello Walkie Talkie<br />\n<br />\n可以將手機化身無線對講機，在烏克蘭革命中廣泛使用，透過Zello可以1對1通話，也可如Telegram 一樣開設頻道（Channel），最多可以與1對千人講話。支援Android、iOS、Blackberry、Windows Phone及Windows等平台。<br />\n<br />\n3. iNtercom<br />\n<br />\n與Zello相同，可當作無線對講機。支援藍牙與Wi-Fi連接，現時Android用戶可免費下載，惟iOS版本要付費，價格為15港元。<br />\n<br />\n4. FireChat<br />\n<br />\n適合在人多、網絡繁忙場所使用，與Bridgefy相同。用家能在FireChat即時建立聊天室討論，最多能讓數以萬計用家同時使用，更可可讓附近用家互傳圖片或文字信息。當越多人使用FireChat時，這點對點無線網絡就會變得更強大。除此之外，FireChat更有私人短訊功能，採用WiFi Direct或藍牙，以「點對點」方式形成一個P2P（Peer-to-Peer）網絡，私人信息會被加密，只有發送者和收件人能查閱。<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nFollow our Instagram @businessfocus.io<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/businessfocus.io/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=5d1e931e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/businessfocus.io/</a><br />\n如欲了解更多財經、商業及創科資訊，<br />\n請於本專頁cover photo下方，按『Following』按鈕然後選擇『See First』<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n若有任何商業、財經及科技資訊的新聞稿，歡迎Inbox或電郵至info@businessfocus.io！<br />\n廣告合作請電郵至sales@businessfocus.io<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n如果你對初創、商業及科技界有所見解，<br />\n敬請投稿至info@businessfocus.io<br />\n歡迎&quot;Join&quot; BF討論區暢談財經、商業及創科話題：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/344368612697900/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F344368612697900%2F&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=8fd0ab84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/344368612697900/</a><br />\n訂閱BusinessFocus YouTube頻道：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.youtube.com/c/BusinessFocus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fc%2FBusinessFocus&d=uCt0JTl3CznPmZ5dgdQegxw%2F%2BIwaTkIdLqRkT71JiWc%3D&h=919bf0a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.youtube.com/c/BusinessFocus</a>"},{"pid":"eae726c48bf3a0ff97bfaac8a95bc91bf05bbbae","tid":1473795,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:07:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n大家揀定用邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a416e0f91d80be33128dd9c1ba503077345e1eb","tid":1473795,"uid":267937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:07:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"897bd08a2702a04174d40ab5bf0c1648e81581e8","tid":1473795,"uid":110313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:09:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a82b7d9ada8adf535dfd043f46fd26fe8e0f346","tid":1473795,"uid":260262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T03:10:11.000Z","msg":"我同班fd 發夢第2日已經有down<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" 